column2: To what extent fundamentals concepts were covered and doubts were cleared?
column3: Competency of the teacher to deal with the course?
column4: Is the lecture interactive, are students encouraged to think and raise the Questions, Doubts?
column5: Are homework/assignment given regularly and assessed properly?
column6: Does the teacher exhibits good Communication, Presentation skill?
column7: Whether Teacher Exhibits Good Behavior and Interaction with Students?
column8: Whether teacher is accessible off classroom hour for counseling and solving Queries?
column9: To what extent are you acquiring the expected skills related to the subject?
column10: How would you rate overall experience in learning this course?
column11: Suggestions if any, to course teacher for improvement.
